            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Calibri' fontsize='8'>Educational attainment varies across STEM fields. Health-related STEM occupations require higher educational qualifications, while other fields show more balanced educational distributions.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
